notes.note:
Good evening, thank you for your previous email with the estimate for the replacement of the starter motor on Gordon's Wrangler. Please be advised, the customer is responsible for any diagnostic fees and shop supplies, as well as a $100 deductible + tax. Additionally, our Mitchell Labour Guide allows for a maximum of 1.6 hours for the starter replacement, and our contract allows for a maximum of $130/h for labour. If you choose to charge the customer the quoted labour rate, the customer will be responsible for the difference. The payout is as follows:

Parts-$329.00
Labour-$208.00 (1.6 hours x $130/h)
Deductible-$100.00 + tax
Tax-$56.81
Authorization-GLPXYBI279

Total = $493.81

Once the repair is complete, please send us a copy of the final invoice for payment.

Best regards, 


Matthew Puls
Claims Adjuster
